Donald Trump woke up in an empty void. It was an endless blackness that expanded as far as the eye can see. A voice thundered from on high. It was maddening, and shook the earth, as it thundered down, &ldquo;WHO DARES CROSS INTO MY REALM?&rdquo;
&quot;I cross into the best realms,&quot; The Don replies.
&quot;W&hellip; WHA&hellip; WHAT?&quot;
A dark figure appeared in the void. Don lifted his eyes to look, and saw Kim Jong-un approaching in a menacing manner, a frown furrowed across his face.
